    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We were bound in Egypt, building for the foe;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God of the Hebrews said, “Let My people go!”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We have crossed the Red Sea, reached the other side;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Pharaoh, his army, perished in the tide."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God of the Hebrews, speak again today;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God of the Hebrews, lead us all the way."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Save all Your people from this crooked age,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Save all Your people from this crooked age."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re released, and now we build the house of God;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His tabernacle is our true abode."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Forty years of oldness left in Jordan’s tide,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Fight we for Canaan on the kingdom side."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Salvation’s Captain sounds the trump of war;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "City by city, take we more and more,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To gain His kingdom, enter into rest,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To gain His kingdom, enter into rest."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What was once God-given soon a form became;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then John the Baptist did God’s word proclaim—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Make another crossing, God is going on;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Judaism’s over; listen to My Son!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Turn from the prophets, turn unto the Son;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s My Beloved, He and I are one;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His Word will save you to the uttermost,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His Word will save you to the uttermost."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now we’re overcomers on the sea of glass;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This final crossing will forever last."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Sing the song of Moses, make the praise complete,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Look! All our enemies beneath our feet."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re overcomers, that’s our real name."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God has His city; Satan gets the shame."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God is our portion for eternity,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God is our portion for eternity."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    }
